\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Feature break-even analysis for Burgers with $r=10$ and $\bar  r=133$. Counting only RHS library features, MPOD reaches the QC-NM-MPOD feature count near $p=15$. Counting decoder features only, MPOD also reaches $\bar  r=133$ secondary degrees of freedom near $p=15$ because $r(p-1)=140$. This feature count does not include the ANN evaluation itself; the ANN adds about $1.43\times 10^5$ dense multiply operations per RHS call before the OpInf feature library is evaluated.}}{15}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:feature_break_even}{{2}{15}{Feature break-even analysis for Burgers with $\qdim =10$ and $\rbar =133$. Counting only RHS library features, MPOD reaches the QC-NM-MPOD feature count near $p=15$. Counting decoder features only, MPOD also reaches $\rbar =133$ secondary degrees of freedom near $p=15$ because $\qdim (p-1)=140$. This feature count does not include the ANN evaluation itself; the ANN adds about $1.43\times 10^5$ dense multiply operations per RHS call before the OpInf feature library is evaluated}{figure.caption.5}{}}
